News & Announcements

  1. Stay up to date with Bay County

  1. Bay County Long-Term Recovery Task Force April 17th 2019

    Bay County Long-Term Recovery Task Force April 17th 2019 Read on...

  2. Six-month Hurricane Michael update presented to Bay County Commission

    Bay County Manager Bob Majka presented a six-month Hurricane Michael update Read on...

  3. Unincorporated Bay County Private Property Debris Removal and Demolition Program

    Bay County is now accepting applications through June 28 for a program that may help private property owners with Hurricane Michael debris removal and/or demolition if they meet certain requirements. Read on...

  4. March 11 begins "last pass" for unincorporated Bay County, Springfield, Callaway, Parker

    “Last pass” for Hurricane Michael debris collection began March 11 for residents of unincorporated Bay County and the cities of Callaway, Parker, Springfield and Mexico Beach. View progress on county-owned roadways at the link below... See the app...

  5. Go Mobile!

    Bay County is proud to announce it has launched a new mobile app! Read on...
